{"tid":390021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食過半年a酸，你問我答","createTime":"2017-09-06T17:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T11:37:07.000Z","uid":17370,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b09c6cafa74ddd92a12fb6b113d13c2dd1910747","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"原來暗瘡問題都幾嚴重，去到上年去睇醫生嗰陣 醫生話都去到第6級，面上長期有5-6粒大既加好多細粒粒同印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問自己都幾貪靚 所以出街都會揸好厚粉遮住 但仍然遮唔到啲凹凹凸凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到上年去睇醫生食左半年a酸 停左到而家已經大半年 暗瘡已經好少再生 係有時食得太多熱氣野會生1粒半粒咁 皮膚好左個人都自信左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由13 14歲生到去上年20歲 我明白生暗瘡係幾咁痛苦 所以想藉住依個post答下大家關於暗瘡或者a酸問題 答到既都盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3defedfd7ceee12e6f95494358bb46662ed19b","tid":390021,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:45:50.000Z","msg":"放低邊度睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錢想睇 唯有排政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4167cdccfeaf13c756b48d17bd105f31bbc98322","tid":390021,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"幾錢，邊度睇"},{"pid":"6decad4dbdcd784dce1d3c8e752cce57a959ac02","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放低邊度睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錢想睇 唯有排政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角陳榮杰<br />\n嗰時乜都唔識 都係上網search見多人話佢ok<br />\n但其實雖然佢覆診唔收診金 但藥費都偏貴<br />\n我覺得可以搵到平啲既<br />\n排政府要等幾耐？"},{"pid":"c096ccc999df01471f08bdfbaba1ff155cb79005","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢，邊度睇</blockquote><br />\n實際價錢唔記得 我一日食20mg一個月好似千幾蚊 第一次睇要俾診金 大概5百幾"},{"pid":"d15c8af2b23112e0efff7b933942528cf646b04f","tid":390021,"uid":104555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:00:47.000Z","msg":"可以確實d講一個月幾多？<br />\n一千幾？<br />\n想比較下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead1a98c520200c505d59d24f219464e3c7cefab","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以確實d講一個月幾多？<br />\n一千幾？<br />\n想比較下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際價錢真係唔太記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係千零左右  千2-千5"},{"pid":"b15ac1731d5a10c020b2be395f08f5fa2a8176c9","tid":390021,"uid":106614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"點去印？"},{"pid":"1e211ac453718df4f87c2b25456c197fd7abec93","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點去印？</blockquote><br />\n我冇特別去處理啲印<br />\n因為當我唔再生既時候 印都慢慢會自己退"},{"pid":"4c3910e6f0b9bd7a63a88a3da711777e7ff7eca9","tid":390021,"uid":81724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"印係紫外光造成， 少曬d就會好d"},{"pid":"5cfcda80f367089e221bf9957cf2bb0a19955b74","tid":390021,"uid":8110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"依家做緊laser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前睇過中西醫, 又唔想食a酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ac44b5d57bce8af7c54c08f1bf645befbf6c3","tid":390021,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"食左幾多個月先開始好轉？"},{"pid":"b2eaf2a5088d6c6cb4b31dee1ae893c875d73d89","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家做緊laser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前睇過中西醫, 又唔想食a酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做laser應該係去印？<br />\n如果仲有keep住生既我覺得處理左暗瘡問題先會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8900caaf9379da52c557d66c3d20f2764164c8f","tid":390021,"uid":1744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:09:49.000Z","msg":"我都食完a酸<br />\n好返好多<br />\n想去印 有咩好介紹"},{"pid":"009efab4c16433e75a1d9388cf478142fce184d3","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左幾多個月先開始好轉？</blockquote><br />\nA酸係我身上既功效好明顯<br />\n我諗我食左幾日已經冇再生新既暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但頭2個月我係有配合埋抗生素食"},{"pid":"110600e0bff88327e34f781394253726d488b01a","tid":390021,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就黎食完第二個月既A 酸，本身右邊面係冇爛既，得一兩粒暗瘡，但爆發期之後右邊面又生多左幾粒，左邊面更加爆到七彩。<br />\n不過我可以肯定既係我冇生暗瘡既地方，d 皮膚好左，毛孔細左，同埋個鼻冇曬粉刺黑頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我四個月後變回一條好漢。<br />\n我睇屋企樓下個普通科醫生，開N 牌A 酸20mg/per day, 一個月$1000連兩細盒藥膏，佢唔收診金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d823072e8dbbd07f58c0324f2693484792d08f8","tid":390021,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以po張前後對比圖出黎振奮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重有4個月A酸要食，食到有d心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e584247fafff4c25422ae02273bc8bd4f17be1","tid":390021,"uid":86775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"留名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係食過四環素，食完3個月就復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6484c3e8713a6c95b261446663ca0192ff3f0ed4","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就黎食完第二個月既A 酸，本身右邊面係冇爛既，得一兩粒暗瘡，但爆發期之後右邊面又生多左幾粒，左邊面更加爆到七彩。<br />\n不過我可以肯定既係我冇生暗瘡既地方，d 皮膚好左，毛孔細左，同埋個鼻冇曬粉刺黑頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我四個月後變回一條好漢。<br />\n我睇屋企樓下個普通科醫生，開N 牌A 酸20mg/per day, 一個月$1000連兩細盒藥膏，佢唔收診金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫生當初有冇問你要唔要埋坑生素？<br />\n因為我就係好驚有爆發期 所以醫生頭2個月開埋抗生素俾我食 <br />\n但巴打你放心 我上年食之前都做過research 爆發期完左就會見到成效咖啦 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ac827d26d5e3a9cef2251eefe468a581c5ae45","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可唔可以po張前後對比圖出黎振奮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重有4個月A酸要食，食到有d心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為覺得爛面時既相好醜 所以del晒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咩心灰意冷 當你食完塊面冇晒暗瘡既時候 會覺得所有野都係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d6e9ed2093784a63b661a35d21d80f4857bf75","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係食過四環素，食完3個月就復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n復發之後既程度有冇比原本好？會唔會考慮食a酸？"},{"pid":"4edc39404874ced145bd0a163cd2267474341c25","tid":390021,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主可唔可以po張前後對比圖出黎振奮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重有4個月A酸要食，食到有d心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為覺得爛面時既相好醜 所以del晒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咩心灰意冷 當你食完塊面冇晒暗瘡既時候 會覺得所有野都係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想睇你塊面而家康復成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efcbda49ae7eb2550c7d1fa18a711de6556fe39","tid":390021,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"你問我唔答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241329971e5f629c871584f075b37cbdf6cf8966","tid":390021,"uid":25903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"食緊 宜家個半月爆到七彩<br />\n越黎越嚴重咁 好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10597630acf0990d8f35f4e7259cda3e09f9bf7e","tid":390021,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"有冇相睇下"},{"pid":"0db921eaa281ce09fef9e5b3577d9ad6549dc9f1","tid":390021,"uid":50666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"我就黎食足一年可以唔使繼續食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9248a062aa4be5f0287520d02bad08a6cefba87b","tid":390021,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"依家用緊咩保養產品"},{"pid":"e225ea738068fb3c2a7b7f367299494d69086318","tid":390021,"uid":133502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"食A酸係咪一定有爆發期? 準備下星期一睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f274c81d630c204cafcaf343f0dcee3dfcbf52f","tid":390021,"uid":142146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"凹凸洞點處理"},{"pid":"1dc57966711d454