core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"有冇副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"848f1f38662e80784c66f195e9672e63269b8fda","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主可唔可以po張前後對比圖出黎振奮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重有4個月A酸要食，食到有d心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為覺得爛面時既相好醜 所以del晒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咩心灰意冷 當你食完塊面冇晒暗瘡既時候 會覺得所有野都係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想睇你塊面而家康復成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔太想放相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之就係已經冇晒瘡但有幾個凹凸洞<br />\n但色素印就已經退得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8bc4f853cc64ea50cc5617ca9658c6f7aff1c7","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就黎食足一年可以唔使繼續食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6836806099e18fe921a7113e8dbc6d49d450be10","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家用緊咩保養產品</blockquote><br />\n醫生介紹用neostrata既果酸產品<br />\n但我覺得食完a酸之後既皮膚乾左 keep住用果酸會有少少甩皮情況 <br />\n所以依排轉左用curel 暫時感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303b0c83f758b65a1ea7b6be0838c48aafebaad0","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食A酸係咪一定有爆發期? 準備下星期一睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定 我配合抗生素食係完全冇爆發期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57352b1fd5567c87a195298e1a264a0f2c954b93","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凹凸洞點處理</blockquote><br />\n我都想知 我都有少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a57c1265d9fdeb31b3bafc3fbb78b4a21968680","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主 有無前後圖睇下 我都睇緊醫生 但唔知佢開緊咩藥</blockquote><br />\n我係食o牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d99e031b6b463b6b328d98db98c0b53563bf31c","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪食晒成個療程(體重x 120)?</blockquote><br />\n唔係啊 只係每日20 食左半年咁<br />\n見已經好番晒就冇跟體重食"},{"pid":"15db7cf881f157f60e5df4090b213b9de5836707","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食緊 一個月1240 o牌 28日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚貴</blockquote><br />\n我同你價錢差唔多<br />\n但我以前未食a酸前都用好多錢去買護膚品搞塊面<br />\n所以覺得每個月俾千幾而真係有幫助既都值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7698bb3f0a42e7abe8db3d33948e6cd2b9f3181","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A酸其實會復發，我食左三次都復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打每次食幾耐同幾多？"},{"pid":"43b241ff4f1ae19ce3c8c5e5661d809984a13ae1","tid":390021,"uid":17370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n最明顯就係皮膚變乾左<br />\n鼻孔都會乾到鼻水都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次仲誇張到流鼻血<br />\n同埋好似話會傷肝 但依樣就唔知啦感覺唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd380db010c90d29272935915ee698874bf0786d","tid":390021,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>A酸其實會復發，我食左三次都復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打每次食幾耐同幾多？</blockquote><br />\n每次食20mg 每個療程都超過一年，依家諗返起好哂錢，依家出返我都冇理佢，由尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52b94de02a9ff94e5b3e2757921162d87a8f56f","tid":390021,"uid":70227,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"我發現好撚多人食左藥就當自己醫生咁亂答<br />\n而唔係叫人睇皮膚科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}